title: Beilein: Irvin should be able to practice by start of season
text: Beilein: Irvin should be able to practice by start of season Saturday, 3 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) ANN ARBOR, Mich. (AP) The optimism surrounding the Michigan basketball team this season is predicated on one main thing - better health for the team's top players.
